Major Contributors
------------------
We like to thank the following people especially, since they made
significant contributions to the Achievo project.

Stefan Niederhauser <sn at atelier-w.ch>

  Stefan came up with the idea and design of the 'node' concept, which
  later became the basis of the ATK backend.

William Rhee <willrhee at umich.edu>

  William, of the University of Michigan, added Oracle 8i Support
  to Achievo.

Marc van Agteren <mva at buzzmachines.com>

  Marc developed the initial version of the finance menu, during
  an internship at ibuildings.nl.

Ludo Beumer <l.m.beumer at home.nl>

  Ludo developed the initial version of the resource planning feature,
  during an internship at ibuildings.nl.


